OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FTravellers to airports are being
OL,8,Fwarned to only pack devices containing
OL,9,Flithium batteries in hand luggage to
OL,10,Freduce the risk of mid-air emergencies.
OL,12,FPower banks, vapes and laptops are
OL,13,Fsome of the devices which use the
OL,14,Ftechnology.
OL,16,FPeople are being urged to think
OL,17,Fcarefully about where they pack their
OL,18,Felectronic devices when going on a
OL,19,Fflight, as the batteries inside them
OL,20,Fnow pose the biggest fire risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
