FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FThere has been a rise in the number of
OL,8,Fflights that have been delayed or
OL,9,Fcancelled because lithium-powered
OL,10,Fitems have been stored in the hold.
OL,12,FNowadays, passengers are carrying as
OL,13,Fmany as four lithium-powered items and
OL,14,Fif they explode in the hold mid-air,
OL,15,Fit's more difficult for aircraft crew
OL,16,Fto deal with.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FWhen ITV Meridian asked passengers at
OL,8,FGatwick Airport if they knew where to
OL,9,Fplace their electronic devices, they
OL,10,Fsaid they knew to put them in hand
OL,11,Fluggage - with some commenting that
OL,12,Fthey had read it in their email.
OL,14,FBut while the the people we asked
OL,15,Fappeared were aware, it's thought that
OL,16,Fmore than of a third of travellers are
OL,17,Fnot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FLithium batteries can also be found in
OL,8,Fitems like bluetooth speakers,
OL,9,Felectric fans, tablets and fitness and
OL,10,Fsmart watches. They are popular
OL,11,Fbecause they can store a lot of energy
OL,12,Fin a small space.
OL,14,FIn 2024 there were 123 reports of
OL,15,Fdevices malfunctioning on UK flights,
OL,16,Fbut that number rose to 206 last year.
OL,18,FOn it's busiest days this summer,
OL,19,FGatwick is expecting 900 flights.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
