OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FIncorrectly packed batteries are not
OL,8,Fonly dangerous, but can cause delays
OL,9,Fand disruption if hold luggage needs
OL,10,Fto be taken off a flight, or if the
OL,11,Fplane is forced to divert.
OL,13,FExperts say the crushing weight of
OL,14,Fbeing in the hold could trigger the
OL,15,Fbatteries to explode - no matter or
OL,16,Fbig or small the device.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FGlenn Bradley from the Civil Aviation
OL,8,FAuthority said: "So many devices have
OL,9,Flithium batteries in it. Quite
OL,10,Fcommonly, people can have full lithium
OL,11,Fbatteries on them, you've got 200
OL,12,Fpeople on an airplane, that's a lot of
OL,13,Fbatteries.
OL,15,F"Now considering that, there isn't
OL,16,Fmany events, but globally we get about
OL,17,Ftwo events a week involved with the
OL,18,Flithium batteries."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FWhen asked if it is important that
OL,8,Fpeople buy from reputable traders, he
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's always good value to buy
OL,10,Fgood quality things.
OL,12,F"We can't legislate for that from an
OL,13,Fairline perspective, but if the
OL,14,Fbattery is carried in the right place
OL,15,Fthen any issue that happens with it
OL,16,Fcan be managed."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
