PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784839668
OL,3,CLithium fire risk warning: Why you
OL,4,Cshould keep batteries in hand luggage
OL,5,Conly
OL,7,FAirlines have brought in new training
OL,8,Fto deal with battery related
OL,9,Femergencies. And the message this
OL,10,Fsummer is to pack right for a safe
OL,11,Fflight
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
